name: Neesha's Story
text: My husband joined the Navy out of this Office a few months ago. through out the whole process they explained everything with great detail and were really nice. They also did their best with educating my husband on all the great job possibilities. Thank you everyone for helping our family!

name: Robert
text: These guys were great when it came to answering my questions, they were happy to help me work with my past issues. Once signed up they had a recruiter who worked out with me so I could get in shape and also would study the stuff they wanted me to know at boot camp

name: Anya babb
text: Petty Officer Johnson is the best Recruter in the world. This office has the best Recruter’s I’ve ever met. They get things done, when you have questions they will answer them at all hours of the day. They will motivate you to work out by pushing your limits to make sure you are ready.

name: Juan Torres
text: These guys are the best. They were informative and really were driven in getting me the job that I wanted!! I am proud to say these guy made me a FUTURE SAILOR!!
